Interface Comparable

public interface netscape.util.Comparable
{
    /* Methods
     */
    public abstract int compareTo(Object);
}
Interface implemented by objects to enable sorting algortithms to sort collections of homogenous instances.

Methods

.compareTo 

  public abstract int compareTo(Object other)
Compares two objects. Returns -1 if "this < other", returns 1 if "this > other", and returns 0 if "this == other". The other object must be the same type as this object, otherwise the ClassCastException is thrown.
Throws: ClassCastException
The other object is not of the same type.
